Labels & Selector:
-------------------

Labels are the mechanism you use to organise kubernetes objects.
This is key value pair. This is similer to Tags in aws.

labels:
	env: Development
	app: Dotnet
-----------------------


apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: nginx-test
  labels:
	 env: Development
	 app: Dotnet
spec:
  containers:
  - name: nginx-test
    image: nginx:1.14.2
    ports:
    - containerPort: 80
	
